{"tid":1391123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年跪求市民支持 8.5 罷工","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:54:09.000Z","uid":130035,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3602ecb7fb07974588da59789dfac71a80a7adfe","tid":1391123,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"反送中觸發的社會運動持續，政府堅拒回應民間訴求，網民發起下周一（8月5日）全港大罷工，並各自自發落區宣傳。今早 9 時，在荃灣愉景新城至港鐵站天橋上，有數名青年人下跪呼籲市民支持罷工。<br />\n一名青年手持標語寫道：「佢願意為香港賭上前途 你願唔願意罷一次工」<br />\n另一標語內容是：<br />\n「如果你心痛，可唔可以返公司組織罷工？<br />\n得你一個罷，我會驚你被秋返算賬，<br />\n但如果你同事、上司都係同路人，我會安心啲。<br />\n8月5 大罷工！」<br />\n有一中年婦女路經時指罵青年影響香港生活，跪地青年持續誠懇解釋和道歉。也有上班族向與青年人說加油打氣。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2kLdNV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2kLdNV.png&h=2805b04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c251428b024e85f68a6c3f68bfc53c80ad6b0703","tid":1391123,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"8cc97f75ae596171b0b6c7fb8b36729fd350d23f","tid":1391123,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"90eb88580bc4054f532b7be6f8598d454c43049e","tid":1391123,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"753f14c2f9d6b985684735180964261467b5fab2","tid":1391123,"uid":130035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"6356db3bd270ae59098d42eb0f24d7e599d00a65","tid":1391123,"uid":108946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dcc