n<br />\n<br />\n試過有法官判示威者以胸部襲警後，相信大家都明白香港有好多紅底法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以獨立調查委員會一定唔可以只係有本地法官組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要嘅獨立調查委員會係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>由國際專家、聯合國，甚至海牙軍事法庭嘅人組成</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>拒絕港共自己人查自己人<br />\n<br />\n要由國際專家調查事件</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598015522b19b78d1b162444c2c45e7eb6ff07e7","tid":1391123,"uid":197096,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"罷工香港點會work 香港人奴性太重 包括我<br />\n身邊同事有家庭有小朋友 點會因為咁就同公司過唔去, 型一日有派你受, 你又控制唔到其他人唔返 你唔返咪又做死其他同事 太多因素令你唔會去罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95ae73863a4de152ca3755df486170f6ba13822","tid":1391123,"uid":92476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"598015522b19b78d1b162444c2c45e7eb6ff07e7","tid":1391123,"uid":197096,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"罷工香港點會work 香港人奴性太重 包括我<br />\n身邊同事有家庭有小朋友 點會因為咁就同公司過唔去, 型一日有派你受, 你又控制唔到其他人唔返 你唔返咪又做死其他同事 太多因素令你唔會去罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"242d4b7c6e3f2092ab78a1cfa15f23945e475438","tid":1391123,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"老細藍不了"},{"pid":"a8f094fb95857e9e169bbd5fd155db5264fbd573","tid":1391123,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":